{"tid":1255384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《紐約時報》正在調查抗議期間警方過度使用武力的指控","createTime":"2019-06-24T13:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T13:30:25.000Z","uid":236703,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e2507c90ca95a28bf37770dda41db7c5bdabe2","tid":1255384,"uid":236703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:06:25.000Z","msg":"在「反送中」遊行抗議期間，您是否親身遭受到了警方的暴力？《紐約時報》正在調查抗議期間警方過度使用武力的指控，如果您在與警方的對抗中嚴重受傷，或認識有類似遭遇的人，請發消息給我們的WhatsApp和Signal：+1 646-951-4771，或者發電郵到tips@nytimes.com。<br />\n<br />\n請給消息添加「Hong Kong」的標籤，並在其中附上盡可能多的細節，如果有照片，也請一並附上。我們的記者可能會聯繫你以瞭解更多詳情。<a href=\"http://nytimes.com/tips\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnytimes.com%2Ftips&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRpktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=2fb14a90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">nytimes.com/tips</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iKUF24F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiKUF24F.png&h=3ae014a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1504603339831430/posts/2192164401075317?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1504603339831430%2Fposts%2F2192164401075317%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRpktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=f3f0ee15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1504603339831430/posts/2192164401075317?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"50d368dceec8d0d6a1298d57210c44c05ca039ad","tid":1255384,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:07:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fcc9232486f3efcff55d1b02665e1158d0643ac5","tid":1255384,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:30:25.000Z","msg":"調查咗會點？"}]}